therefore becomes
"Let ([ CLNum = 1 ] ; GetNthRecord ( Field ; CLNum )) & ¶ &
Let ([ CLNum = 2 ] ; GetNthRecord ( Field ; CLNum )) & ¶ &
Let ([ CLNum = 3 ] ; GetNthRecord ( Field ; CLNum )) & ¶ &
Let ([ CLNum = 4 ] ; GetNthRecord ( Field ; CLNum ))"

2/ Evaluates this chain.

Interrested in the mechanism ?
